      "text": "[[Christine Wertheim]] is a faculty member of the School of Critical Studies at the California Institute of the Arts where she teaches writing, literature, and critical theory. Her most recent articles on art and aesthetics have appeared in X-tra and in Art Seminar, an anthology forthcoming from Routledge. In 2004, she organized “Séance,” a two-day conference at REDCAT on the conditions of language and narrative in contemporary writing. She is co-director of the Institute For Figuring."
